S6E1.title: The One with the Princess Leia Fantasy
S6E1.des:
Ross reveals a fantasy to Rachel involving a
                certain Star Wars character.

S6E2.title: The One Where No One's Ready
S6E2.des:
In a race against the clock, Ross tries to get
                the gang dressed and ready for a black-tie benefit at the museum.

S6E3.title: The One with the Jam
S6E3.des:
After breaking up with Richard, Monica uses her
                free time to make jam and consider insemination via a sperm bank.

S6E4.title: The One with the Metaphorical Tunnel
S6E4.des:
Ross panics when he sees his son with a Barbie
                doll. Phoebe poses as Joey's agent and gets him some good parts.

S6E5.title: The One with Frank Jr
S6E5.des:
Phoebe's half-brother visits, and they have
                trouble bonding.

S6E6.title: The One with the Flashback
S6E6.des:
When Janice asks the gang if any of them have
                ever slept together, the friends flash back to a time three years earlier.

S6E7.title: The One with the Race Car Bed
S6E7.des:
Monica buys a new bed from Janice's
                soon-to-be-ex-husband, but the wrong one is delivered.

S6E8.title: The One with the Giant Poking Device
S6E8.des:
Joey and Monica catch Janice kissing her
                ex-husband.

S6E9.title: The One with the Football
S6E9.des:
The gang plays a game of touch football on
                Thanksgiving.

S6E10.title: The One Where Rachel Quits
S6E10.des:
Rachel quits her job after Gunther tells her she
                needs to be retrained.

S6E11.title:
The One Where Chandler Can't Remember Which
                    Sister
S6E11.des:
A drunken Chandler fools around with one of
                Joey's sisters -- but he can't remember which one.

S6E12.title: The One with All the Jealousy
S6E12.des:
Ross becomes jealous when he thinks he catches
                Rachel's new co-worker flirting with her.

S6E13.title:
The One Where Monica & Richard Are Just
                    Friends
S6E13.des:
Monica's willpower is tested when she runs into
                Richard at a video store.

S6E14.title: The One with Phoebe's Ex-Partner
S6E14.des:
Phoebe is reunited with her former singing
                partner. Rachel's new job is putting a strain on her relationship with Ross.

S6E15.title: The One Where Ross & Rachel Take a Break
S6E15.des:
Ross seeks solace at a party after a bitter
                fight with Rachel and ends up in the arms of another woman.

S6E16.title: The One The Morning After
S6E16.des:
When Rachel discovers that Ross slept with
                Chloe, she decides to break up with him.

S6E17.title: The One Without the Ski Trip
S6E17.des:
A lonely Ross visits Carol when Rachel goes on a
                ski trip with some friends.

S6E18.title: The One with the Hypnosis Tape
S6E18.des:
Phoebe is distraught when her brother wants to
                marry a woman twice his age. A hypnosis tape makes Chandler act like a woman.

S6E19.title: The One with the Tiny T-Shirt
S6E19.des:
Rachel goes on her first date since her breakup
                with Ross. Monica dates Pete, even though she is still not attracted to him.

S6E20.title: The One with the Dollhouse
S6E20.des:
Joey thinks he's found his true love. Rachel's
                boss dates Chandler, creating big trouble for Rachel. Monica inherits a dollhouse.

S6E21.title: The One with a Chick. And a Duck
S6E21.des:
When Pete buys a restaurant, Monica must decide
                whether to accept his offer of employment there. Joey and Chandler adopt a duck and a chick.

S6E22.title: The One with the Screamer
S6E22.des:
Ross thinks that Rachel's date is crazy. Joey
                falls in love with Kate, but when she's offered a job in Los Angeles, she takes it.

S6E23.title: The One with Ross's Thing
S6E23.des:
Ross finds a strange growth on his buttocks.
                Phoebe can't choose between two guys. Monica's boyfriend surprises her by not proposing marriage.

S6E24.title: The One with the Ultimate Fighting Champion
S6E24.des:
To Monica's horror, Pete plans to be in an
                ultimate fight. Phoebe sets Ross up on a date with a woman who used to be bald.

S6E25.title: The One at the Beach
S6E25.des:
The gang goes to the beach. Phoebe meets a
                family friend with links to her family's past. Ross discovers that Rachel still loves him.

year:
The shenanigans of the tightest circle of friends --
            including Chandler and Joey adopting a duck -- continue as Season 3 plays out.
about:
The shenanigans of the tightest circle of friends --
            including Chandler and Joey adopting a duck -- continue as Season 3 plays out.
